---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy policy for DevTools - Your data stays in your browser."
>
  <article class="prose prose-slate dark:prose-invert max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    
    <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> {new Date().toLocaleDateString()}</p>
    
    <h2>Data Collection</h2>
    <p>
      DevTools does not collect, store, or transmit any user data. All processing happens entirely 
      in your browser using client-side JavaScript.
    </p>
    
    <h2>Analytics</h2>
    <p>
      We may use analytics services (like Cloudflare Analytics or Google Analytics) to understand 
      how visitors use our site. This data is anonymized and does not include personal information.
    </p>
    
    <h2>Cookies</h2>
    <p>
      We use local storage to remember your theme preference (light/dark mode). This data stays 
      on your device and is never transmitted.
    </p>
    
    <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>
      We may display advertisements through third-party ad networks. These services may use 
      cookies and tracking technologies. Please review their privacy policies.
    </p>
    
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      If you have questions about this privacy policy, please contact us through our GitHub repository.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>


